  "3199360": {
    "name": "骷髅成群",
    "steam_appid": 3199360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在《骷髅成群》将化身飞天骷髅死灵法师，召集骷髅军队，对抗无穷无尽的邪恶肉躯。探索程序生成的地城，同时获得战利品，组建你的战队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/fe60a102b92369da8862a9a8195a5a18.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/c9fb4f0021cb21cb5f9c36b024ce5108.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索程序生成的各种地城，每种地城敌人各不相同，需要不同的策略应对。这些地城可以发现宝箱与神台，获得强大的战利品和奖励，不过你必须时刻移动，否则就有可能无法招架敌人的攻势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/c6acc269db2a3303a80dc87b325e68ec.poster.avif?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/c6acc269db2a3303a80dc87b325e68ec.webm?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/c6acc269db2a3303a80dc87b325e68ec.mp4?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/fe60a102b92369da8862a9a8195a5a18.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/cf1cda3ae6815faf66b3e4efb11f3f85.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏全程都有机会购买多种单位，组建你的战队。各种单位的特殊能力各不相同，以便你打造具备强大协同效应的队伍。同种单位购买多个之后，会融合成为更强的版本，最终将解锁独一无二的特殊能力。地城获得的战利品会与单位的种类和标签产生互动，从而产生强大的效果。巧妙利用资源，合理刷新单位和战利品，以便精准打造你所寻找的构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/a4ff27ae10dfbfb3eda4467d8a32f091.poster.avif?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/a4ff27ae10dfbfb3eda4467d8a32f091.webm?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/a4ff27ae10dfbfb3eda4467d8a32f091.mp4?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/fe60a102b92369da8862a9a8195a5a18.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/211f2b97c5e3aff922b03412430604b0.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏实时运行，你的随从会自己战斗。你的作用是组建战队，决定探索哪里，什么时候继续前进，还有选择正确的升级项目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/b95d87dce97e59bfeb02708473831053.poster.avif?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/b95d87dce97e59bfeb02708473831053.webm?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/b95d87dce97e59bfeb02708473831053.mp4?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/fe60a102b92369da8862a9a8195a5a18.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/47ab29b32e4943e9ca158571728f29fa.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着不断成长，你将解锁强力效果，可以在每局游戏开始时选择。不同玩家角色的长处不同，将他们的长处与所选效果结构，就能为强大的构筑奠定基础。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种地城都会有一套挑战等你完成。每一套挑战都需要不同的策略，也会让你获得新的解锁项目和内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/ec4a246be1a8f09339df1ff4d6e2bee5.poster.avif?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/ec4a246be1a8f09339df1ff4d6e2bee5.webm?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/ec4a246be1a8f09339df1ff4d6e2bee5.mp4?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/fe60a102b92369da8862a9a8195a5a18.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/9ea272fad279eb612e2c8d9c29423503.webp?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地城程序生成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实时自动战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许多关卡，敌人种类各不相同</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同角色，各有各的特殊能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种单位，可以融合成为更强版本，获得特殊能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量强力战利品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强大的特殊效果</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种挑战需要有创意的构筑才能克服</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/56c79a2e372fa9c8bb35ae63c1d08922.poster.avif?t=1770039254\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/56c79a2e372fa9c8bb35ae63c1d08922.webm?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199360/extras/56c79a2e372fa9c8bb35ae63c1d08922.mp4?t=1770039254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
